                     <summary>Incredibly elaborate monument. The top three points of the cross have trefoil and botchered trefoil decoration as well as a cherubs head with wings. At the centre of the cross is a metallic sculpture of Christ, seated on a stone pulpit. He has a halo on his head, and his right arm is held out while his left is resting on an orb. Below this there is a metal chi-rho and alpha-omega. Below this is a matal garland.</summary>
